{"tid":1983350,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"（新手）passive speakers點樣駁落電腦好？","createTime":"2020-04-21T18:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T11:49:06.000Z","uid":30410,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0a3886dd372f05daca87c7ba6eb47db8f2b8a434","tid":1983350,"uid":30410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T18:42:34.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n之前淘左部卡啦ok點歌機放係倉到玩<br />\n因為set咪要駁amp所以就順便淘左set amp&amp;passive speaker<br />\n咁而家個倉無租了<br />\n部點歌機又賣左出去得番set  amp連speaker放左係屋企<br />\n原本屋企用緊mircolab既m200 2.1<br />\n咁我就拆左佢左右喇叭就咁買左對紅白線駁住m200同個amp<br />\n大致上就係<br />\n電腦(1條3.5mm)&gt;m200(1對2條紅白綫)&gt;amp（2對喇叭線）&gt;passive speaker<br />\n搞到而家枱底成堆線亂到爆炸兼個speaker又多電流聲又間唔中一邊無聲<br />\n<br />\n請問有無D方法可以令對speaker直接駁電腦/起碼唔洗駁住mircolab部機先/改善到speaker間中一邊無聲依個問題？"},{"pid":"128c51f8908f56fde76b7be6fcdec33ab477d647","tid":1983350,"uid":354823,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T18:46:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5188a65b6902212b6d87bc8d9989198ba9df9790","tid":1983350,"uid":30410,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"128c51f8908f56fde76b7be6fcdec33ab477d647","tid":1983350,"uid":354823,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T18:46:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T19:12:50.000Z","msg":"會駁m200有2個原因<br />\n1當時搬set野番屋企咩線都無係手，咪求奇拆對舊dvd機既3色線去駁amp<br />\n2 m200個音量控制旋鈕好細好好用可以再駁3.5mm headset and line in(依個唔firm)<br />\n<br />\n假如照你咁講3.5mm to 2rca<br />\n有無D係3.5mm female to 2rca可以介紹比我？我會另外配番個音量控制旋鈕"},{"pid":"e827ed9a46711f21915d826bef3f442d7d65430d","tid":1983350,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T00:56:07.000Z","msg":"你有sound card/dac?<br />\n定底板直出?"},{"pid":"aa790fcf4930bb512928606152d11cf855e7861f","tid":1983350,"uid":30410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e827ed9a46711f21915d826bef3f442d7d65430d","tid":1983350,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T00:56:07.000Z